
## Instalação no seu Projeto Adianti

```bash
# Via Composer (após publicar no GitHub)
composer config repositories.tfancytree vcs https://github.com/marcelonees/tfancytree
composer require marcelonees/tfancytree:dev-main

# Ou instalação manual
git clone https://github.com/marcelonees/tfancytree.git
cp -r tfancytree/src/* lib/
cp -r tfancytree/assets/* public/assets/